            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5343271-jen-o?shelf=1st-in-series">1st-in-series</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5343271-jen-o?shelf=not-at-my-library">not-at-my-library</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5343271-jen-o?shelf=supernatural">supernatural</a>, 
